    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "It seems the archaeologist #p512# in the Rocky Mountains on the East side of Perion has another request."
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "#b#p512# the Archeologist#k said that it is not safe to leave the valuable fossils in the tent. He asked me to take the fossils and deliver them to #bDr. #p308##k in #m10002000#. He also wrote a letter of introduction for me to show her. "
    },
    "2": {
      "_dirName": "2",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "#b#p512# the Archeologist#k in Perion said that it is not safe to leave the valuable fossils in his tent. He asked me to deliver them to #bDr. #p308##k in #m10002000#. Dr. #p308# said she's going to be really busy from now, and she asked me to stop by again and give her a hand afterwards. Fossils huh...? Should I give it a try?"
    },
