  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Oh my, these are it! Thank you so much, I finally got them back thanks to you. Phew, that saved me from losing my years of work. Since you did such a fine job recovering those for me... can you help me out one more time?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Thank you so much. You're unlike any of the young people that seem so selfish and self-absorbed. I think leaving the fossils that you worked hard to recover here in the tent is too dangerous. I don't know when the monsters will raid again, but I can't leave this place. I have more fossils to recover."
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Please give this letter of introduction to #bDr. #p308##k of #m10002000#, who's a renowned biologist. And please give this #b#t4031071##k to her. Thank you, and good luck."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "I may have asked you for too big a favor. I'm sure you must be busy and all. I may have to ask someone else for this. Take care then."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Dr. #p512# sent you for me? He must be at Perion recovering fossils..."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Ohh, these are the fossils. Seeing the letter, it looks like Dr. #p512# trusts you quite a bit. I may need some help once I start investigating these, so please drop by and see me if you have some time. This is the reward for your job well done. I'll see you around."
        }
      },
      "stop": {
        "_dirName": "stop",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "sub"
        },
        "item": {
          "_dirName": "item",
          "_dirType": "sub",
          "0": {
            "_dirName": "0",
            "_dirType": "String",
            "_value": "And... who are you?? I'm a very busy person, and if you don't have anything for me, please leave. When is the person that Dr. #p512# sent coming?"
          }
        }
      },
      "lost": {
        "_dirName": "lost",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "I think you left this here... you have to be more careful than that."
        },
